						               													<description>Race. Hack. Win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Reality Shift, race across large magnetic Reality Cubes while hacking into them to change their positions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Move your light bike across any side of the cubes to find the best path to the finish.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Shift reality by hacking the track to slide, rotate, flip and tilt the Reality Cubes. Block your opponents&amp;rsquo; paths, make your path to the finish shorter, or crush your opponents!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Reality Shift is a fast-paced 3D racing game for 2 to 4 players set in a retro virtual reality world. The racetrack is made of cubes whose magnetic facings have different paths on them. Your light bike is not constrained by gravity. Your magnetic figure can use any accessible path on the tops and the sides of the cubes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Being fast is not enough though. You will be able to play a card each turn that will move a Reality Cube, creating a track that is always shifting. Don&amp;rsquo;t have a path to the finish? Transform the board to make one. Is an opponent in the lead? Change the track to block their way or just crush them with a Reality Cube, forcing them to respawn at the start.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be faster, smarter, and more ruthless than the other racers to win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Deluxe Components included:&amp;#10;- 1 White Light Bike and summary card&amp;#10;- 21 Power Cube counters&amp;#10;- 1 Double-sided grid board&amp;#10;- 18 Power-up cards&amp;#10;- 1 Vortex Cube&amp;#10;- 1 White Hole Cube&amp;#10;- 1 Portal Cube&amp;#10;- 1 Deluxe Rulebook&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The cubes can be added to a base game setup providing you with new hazards and options while the Power-up cards provide new variants to include in a race.  The grid board allows for a basic side or one with track movement layouts that can be used in conjunction with cube movement.  The White Light Bike is powerful if chosen but comes with a few built-in setbacks as well.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The deluxe rulebook comes with 11 new track setups for use with the deluxe set or in combination with the retail version allowing for larger tracks.  It also details all the variations and power-up card descriptions as well as rules for including a 5th player using the white Light Bike.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
